Package: statsguider
Type: Package
Title: Guided Statistical Test Selection with a Minimal Branching Workflow
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Dai", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "daik54015@gmail.com")
Description: Provides a minimal, rule-based workflow for selecting simple
    statistical tests from a data frame. The package focuses on single-outcome
    group comparisons, keeps the argument contract small, executes only a
    limited set of base-R methods, and redirects users when a simple test is
    not the right analysis branch.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/dai540/statsguider,
